        "text": "Elpaal.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " From ver. 12 to ver. 28 we have a numerous list of his descendants, evidently in different degrees of relationship, but with the thread picked up apparently several times, in the persons of the first-mentioned \"sons,\" viz. the five, ",
        "children": []
      },
