        "element": "span",
        "class": "cmt_word",
        "text": "Ono and Lod",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". These places are not mentioned in Joshua as originally assigned to Benjamin. They were obtained or \"built\" afterwards. They are first mentioned in this passage, afterwards in ",
